column2: entryBytes        The amount of VM heap currently used by regions configured for eviction.
column3: lruEvictions        Number of total entry evictions triggered by LRU.
column4: lruDestroys        Number of entries destroyed in the region through both destroy cache operations and eviction. Reset to zero each time it exceeds lruDestroysLimit.
column5: lruDestroysLimit        Maximum number of entry destroys triggered by LRU before scan occurs.
column6: lruEvaluations        Number of entries evaluated during LRU operations.
column7: lruGreedyReturns        Number of non-LRU entries evicted during LRU operations
